Laparoscopic cautery in the treatment of endometriosis-related infertility.

Murphy AA(1), Schlaff WD, Hassiakos D, Durmusoglu F, Damewood MD, Rock JA.

Author information:
(1)Department of Gynecology and Obstetrics, Johns Hopkins University, Baltimore, 
