Comment in
    Fertil Steril. 1991 Sep;56(3):579-82.

Life table analysis and the two-parameter exponential method have been applied 
to pregnancy rates in 72 patients undergoing laparoscopic cautery exclusively. 
Patients with male factor infertility were excluded. Estimated cure rates for 
